problem: Great Grandma Jones has 6426947 children.  And each of her children has 6426947 children of their own, who are Great Grandma Jones' grandchildren.  And each of these grandchildren has 6426947 babies of their own, who are Great Grandma Jones' great grand-babies.  If all of the family show up at the family reunion, how many great grand-babies will be there for Great Grandma Jones to kiss?
